room_title: Escape room "National Treasure" by The Escape Room Woodbridge in New Brunswick
room_description: While on vacation with a group of your buddies you are called to duty. The mission is to break into the office of a senior government official and steal Top-Secret files which contain our nations deepest secrets. You have 60 minutes to recover the files and get your buddies to the to the private airstrip safely. Can you make it in 60 minutes?
